{"title_page": "Gabriel Montiel Guti\u00e9rrez", "text_new": "{{Spanish name|Montiel|Guti\u00e9rrez}}\n{{Infobox YouTube personality gay\n|name            = Gabriel Montiel\n|image           = Gaborever.jpg\n|image_size      = \n|caption         = \n|channel_name    = Werevertumorro\n|channel_name2   = Gaborever \n|channel_name3   = xvideos.com\n<!-- DO NOT ADD A PERIOD/FULL STOP here as this parameter serves as a link to the channel, and the youtube url does not include a period/full stop -->\n|birth_name      = Gabriel Montiel Guti\u00e9rrez\n|birth_date      = {{birth date and age|1989|9|23|df=yes}}<ref>Rosie Matheson. ''YouTube Famous: Making it big on the internet.'' 2015. Available at [https://books.google.com/books?id=lggxCgAAQBAJ&pg=Hola05&lpg=PT105 Google Books].</ref>\n|birth_place     = [[Mexico City]], [[Mexico]]<ref>http://www.elquehaydecierto.cl/noticia/sociedad/hola-soy-german-comparte-detalles-de-su-infancia-en-copiapo-video</ref><ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=58&v=h8WEzaGAjm4</ref>\n|associated_acts =  Alejandro Montiel (brother)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/espectaculos/2014/impreso/hermano-de-werever-cambia-de-canal-130314.html|title=Hermano de Werever cambia de canal|language=Spanish|date=5 April 2014|accessdate=31 December 2019|first1=Cristina|last1=Pineda|first2=Sughey|last2=Ba\u00f1os|first3=Ariel|last3=Le\u00f3n|work=[[El Universal (Mexico City)|El Universal]]}}</ref>\n|origin          = Mexico City\n|height          = 1.78 m\n|nationality     = Mexican\n|years_active    = 2007\u2013present\n|genre           = [[Comedy]], [[video blog]], [[Video game|gaming]]\n|creator         = Gabriel Montiel\n|views           = 2.64 billion (Werevertumorro)\n|view_date       = as of 11 July 2019<ref name=\"vistatsx\"/>\n|subscribers     = 16.51 million (Werevertumorro)\n|subscriber_date = As of 11 July 2019<ref name=vistatsx>{{cite web|url=http://vidstatsx.com/youtube-top-100-most-subscribed-channels|title=YouTube Top 100 Most Subscribed Channels List - Top by Subscribers|work=vidstatsx.com|accessdate=10 September 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171227185133/http://vidstatsx.com/youtube-top-100-most-subscribed-channels|archive-date=27 December 2017|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n}}\n\n'''Gabriel Montiel Guti\u00e9rrez''' (born 23 September 1989), better known by his pseudonyms '''Werevertumorro''' and '''Gaborever''',  is a Mexican [[YouTube]]r whose channel primarily consists of [[videoblogs|vlogs]] and [[gameplay]]s. Also is a former [[association football|footballer]] who played as a [[Midfielder#Defensive midfielder|Defensive Midfielder]] for [[Murci\u00e9lagos F.C.|Murci\u00e9lagos]] in the [[Liga Premier de Ascenso]] ([[Segunda Divisi\u00f3n de M\u00e9xico|Third division]] of Mexican Football).\n\n==Club career==\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name        = Gabriel Montiel Guti\u00e9rrez\n| image       = \n| image_size  = 200\n| caption     = \n| fullname    = Gabriel Montiel Guti\u00e9rrez<ref name=\"Profile\">{{cite web|title=Gabriel Montiel profile|url=http://www.ligabbva.mx/cancha/jugador/63692/gabriel-montiel-gutierrez|publisher=Liga BBVA MX website|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n| birth_date  = {{birth date and age|df=y|1989|9|23}}<ref name=\"Profile\" />\n| birth_place = [[Ciudad de M\u00e9xico]], [[M\u00e9xico]]\n| height      = 1.78 m<ref name=\"Profile\" />\n| position    = \n| currentclub =\n| clubnumber  = \n| youthyears1 = \n| youthclubs1 = \n| years1 = 2014\n| clubs1  = [[Murci\u00e9lagos F.C.|Murci\u00e9lagos]]\n| caps1  = 1\n| goals1 = 0\n| totalcaps = 1\n| totalgoals = 0\n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1  = \n| nationalcaps1  = \n| nationalgoals1 = \n| club-update    = 29 August 2014\n| nationalteam-update = \n}}\n\n===\u00c1guilas de Teotihuac\u00e1n===\nGuti\u00e9rrez began his career at 16 playing for [[Arcesvids]]'s affiliate youth team \u00c1guilas de Teotihuac\u00e1n. He made his debut during the Apertura 2007 season, August 18, 2007 in a 3-0 defeat against Real Olmec Sport. He scored his first goal on September 19, 2007 against [[Tolcayuca]] in a 1-0 win for \u00c1guilas. He made a second goal October 10, 2007 against Real Halcones, the match ended in a 2-2 draw. In total Guti\u00e9rrez made 12 appearances and 2 goals for \u00c1guilas de Teotihuac\u00e1n.\n\n===Murci\u00e9lagos===\nOn 7 August 2014, Guti\u00e9rrez announced on Twitter that he was joining [[Murci\u00e9lagos F.C.]] for the [[:es:Torneo 2014-2015 Segunda Divisi\u00f3n de M\u00e9xico|Apertura 2014]] season, alongside his mate Israel Rivera, who also takes part of Werevertumorro Crew. Gabriel only played for 3 minutes in the game played against [[Universidad Aut\u00f3noma de Zacatecas]], the final result was 1-1.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mexico.cnn.com/entretenimiento/2014/08/07/werevertumorro-de-videobloguero-estrella-a-futbolista-de-segunda|title=Werevertumorro, de bloguero de primera a futbolista de Segunda|publisher=|accessdate=15 January 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140824163632/http://mexico.cnn.com/entretenimiento/2014/08/07/werevertumorro-de-videobloguero-estrella-a-futbolista-de-segunda|archive-date=24 August 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n==Career statistics==\n\n===Club===\n{{updated|29 August 2014}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Club performance\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | Cup\n\n! colspan=2 | Continental\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n! Season !! Club !! League\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Mexico\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | Cup\n\n! colspan=2 | [[CONCACAF Champions League|North America]]\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n|[[:es:Torneo 2014-2015 Segunda Divisi\u00f3n de M\u00e9xico|2014-15]]||rowspan=\"1\"|[[Murci\u00e9lagos F.C.|Murci\u00e9lagos]]||rowspan=\"1\"|[[Liga Premier de Ascenso]]||1||0||-||-||-||-||1||0\n|-\n!| Total\n! colspan=1 | Mexico\n!1||0||0||0||0||0||0||1\n|0\n|}\n\n== References 